examples: Plans were being made for the construction of a new interstate highway system.
Se estaban haciendo planes para la construcción de un nuevo sistema de carreteras interestatales.
Highway patrol officers closed the road.
Los agentes de la patrulla de carreteras cerraron la carretera.
A parked car was obstructing the highway.
Un automóvil estacionado obstruía la carretera.
there was a crash involving five cars on the highway into the city.
Hubo un accidente que involucró a cinco autos en la carretera hacia la ciudad.
